WEBVTT

00:00.407 --> 00:02.386
Previously on "For the People"...

00:03.360 --> 00:04.427
Damn!

00:04.461 --> 00:06.606
I can cancel my date tonight
and work on this with you.

00:06.630 --> 00:08.106
I don't want you to cancel your date.

00:08.131 --> 00:10.333
I'll be thinking about you
the whole time.

00:10.367 --> 00:12.335
It's about opposing counsel.
She's my girlfriend.

00:12.369 --> 00:13.869
The AUSA handling the case

00:13.904 --> 00:16.204
filed the additional claims
for the sole purpose

00:16.239 --> 00:17.974
of pressuring Ms. Locarno into a deal.

00:18.008 --> 00:19.976
- I'm on probation.
- I did what I had to do.

00:20.010 --> 00:22.021
And now I'm gonna do
what I have to do. I'm leaving.

00:22.045 --> 00:23.323
- Good morning.
- Not for you, apparently.

00:23.347 --> 00:24.524
We were just talking about losers.

00:24.548 --> 00:26.693
My case was thrown out.
Can we really call that a loss?

00:26.717 --> 00:27.883
We can call it a big loss.

00:27.918 --> 00:30.319
We are not going to break up
over an insidertrading case.

00:30.354 --> 00:31.531
No, we're gonna break up because

00:31.555 --> 00:33.889
I don't want to be second chair
to you the rest of my life.

00:33.924 --> 00:35.958
And if I stay,
we both know that I would be.

